elements.name: Patient can view appointment notification and invoice in notifications icon and  in home page notifications panel

steps.name: Patient was on homepage
gets the number on notification icon
gets the count of notifications by accessing notification icon
Patient clicks on Online Portal
Patient clicks on Book Appointment
chooses Payer Type as "Patient"
Appointment Type as "Consultation"
Patient should be navigated to Appointment filters page and see a message "Please use the filters if you wish to refine your search"

arguments.val: Please use the filters if you wish to refine your search

steps.name: Patient clicks on Search button
Appointment search Results should be displayed
Patient clicks on "1" available appointment details
Patient sees a message "The patient will be charged at 10% of the full price plus £50.00 fixed fee if you cancel the appointment within 1 hours." on Appointment Details page

arguments.val: The patient will be charged at 10% of the full price plus £50.00 fixed fee if you cancel the appointment within 1 hours.

steps.name: Patient clicks on Book Appointment button on Details Page
Appointment Booking Complete confirmation message "was successfully completed" should be displayed
Patient clicks on Online Portal
the number on notification icon should be increased by refreshing the page
Patient clicks on Notifications icon and clicks on All Notifications in dropdown menu
Patient should view appointment notification and invoice for newly booked appointment in notifications
